@node registrazione Registration.
REGISTRATION.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
To get the registred version of Telemako is needed a payment of
10$ (ten U.S.D.)  or italian Lit.14.000.
Also is possible to exchange the program with the equivalent amount
in blank marked disks, audio or VHS cassettes, CD/LP of heavy metal
or latest techno music and guitar tablature of Manowar, Nirvana,
Iron Maiden, Scorpions...

To receive the program is necessary send me your form of payment to the
address below, including the @{" registration module " link modulo}.

